Clio,is,a,legal,practice,management,system,suitable,for,small,to,mid,sized,law,firms,It,offers,a,suite,of,tools,to,help,users,manage,their,practice,including,document,management,time,tracking,billing,scheduling,and,more,The,Clio,API,allows,users,to,access,functionality,of,the,system,and,data,stored,within,Functionality,includes,operations,on,activities,bills,contacts,matters,tasks,and,users,The,API,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,JSON